{"tid":1536310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從渣男到球迷會 － 表態後的後續","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:39:57.000Z","uid":305482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ab488ee51393743a8b2f9d1385fc5ad0954d8c96","tid":1536310,"uid":305482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:27:18.000Z","msg":"馬後炮都要講<br />\n<br />\n大家希望不同團體表態<br />\n<br />\n但表態完之後五毛玻璃心就會做野<br />\n<br />\n好似球迷會咁，自己友退出官方後，香港五毛一定再搞一個，到時香港既官方球迷會係五毛玩灑，自己友反而要變地底<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天主教係國內情況大家有眼睇<br />\n<br />\n所以大家再諗下黎緊係唔係仲要人表態<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pnutiwV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpnutiwV.png&h=ee32751f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sx4EqbX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSx4EqbX.png&h=ce53ea48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cf9665e7537d30b329e5224a7627a9d9481a7bf","tid":1536310,"uid":305482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:27:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c38f2cb349146e35446af91b1cf8e89505dd63f2","tid":1536310,"uid":305482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f666eccb90eb6957d2f6fd098cbd1d46f52ab304","tid":1536310,"uid":305482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:28:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7ac3e2fb00ce9795abaa8f59f13c708a5e15a83c","tid":1536310,"uid":305482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:28:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a2c298caf8f8030585205de9c56e379fbe689dc3","tid":1536310,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:29:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01a95eab6b25c3a6a924a1d721357518401fdb5f","tid":1536310,"uid":305482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:29:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e5978c044c8032ed9ec4dc55c897395ec0c9d602","tid":1536310,"uid":167883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Renq43y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRenq43y.jpg&h=bb73b46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2FTuve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2FTuve.jpg&h=3a22dffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xbetioz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxbetioz.jpg&h=8f95a040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1513398/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https:/